%20is%20full%20of%20craters%20and%20deep%20trenches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpace%20agency%20ISRO%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20landing%20will%20take%20place%20without%20a%20hitch%2C%20as%20the%20scientists%20have%20incorporated%20all%20the%20valuable%20lessons%20they%20learnt%20from%20Chandrayaan-2.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20event%20will%20begin%20at%205.20%20pm%20by%20the%20ISRO%20website%2C%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20DD%20National.%20%C2%A0At%206.04%20pm%2C%20the%20Vikram%20lander%2C%20carrying%20the%20rover%20Pragyaan%2C%20will%20attempt%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20moon's%20South%20Pole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20location%20has%20been%20chosen%20with%20care.%20The%20area%2C%20which%20yielded%20traces%20of%20water%2C%20is%20expected%20hold%20the%20key%20on%20lunar%20water%20ice%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20hugely%20valuable%20resource.%20That%20there%20is%20water%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface%20was%20detected%20by%20a%20NASA%20instrument%20aboard%20the%20ISRO's%20Chandrayaan-1%20probe%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20presence%20of%20water%20holds%20hope%20for%20future%20moon%20missions%20-%20it%20could%20be%20used%20as%20a%20source%20of%20drinking%20water%2C%20to%20cool%20equipment%20and%20broken%20down%20to%20produce%20oxygen.%20It%20can%20also%20have%20clues%20to%20the%20origins%20of%20oceans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20will%20be%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20land%20a%20rover%20on%20moon%20after%20Russia%2C%20United%20States%20and%20China.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EISRO%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20mission%20is%20on%20schedule%20and%20systems%20are%20undergoing%20regular%20checks.%20%26quot%3BSmooth%20sailing%20is%20continuing.%20The%20Mission%20Operations%20Complex%20(at%20ISRO)%20is%20buzzed%20with%20energy%20and%20excitement!%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20ISRO%20also%20released%20images%20of%20the%20moon%20photographed%20from%20a%20height%20of%20around%2070%20km.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20moon%20lander%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%2C%20perched%20on%20a%20LVM%203%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle.%20It%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%205.%20The%20lander%20Vikram%20is%20named%20after%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%2C%20who%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20moon%20mission%2C%20ISRO%20has%20a%20number%20of%20projects%20lined%20up%20-%20one%20of%20them%20a%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20and%20a%20human%20space%20flight%20programme%2C%20Gaganyaan.%20Aditya-L1%2C%20the%20first%20space-based%20Indian%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20is%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20launch%2C%20most%20likely%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692754740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F0hrs7a18_chandrayaan3-moon-shot_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-landing-india-ready-for-moon-touchdown-this-evening-10-points-4320885%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20keeping%20its%20fingers%20crossed%20as%20moon%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20set%20to%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20this%20evening.%20Parties%20and%20prayers%20are%20being%20held%20with%20equal%20fervour%2C%20with%20scientists%20predicting%20%26quot%3B20%20minutes%20of%20terror%26quot%3B%20before%20the%20touchdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-landing-india-ready-for-moon-touchdown-this-evening-10-points-4320885%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-landing-india-ready-for-moon-touchdown-this-evening-10-points-4320885%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-landing-india-ready-for-moon-touchdown-this-evening-10-points-4320885%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIn%20One%20Click...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Bats%20For%20UPI's%20Global%20Expansion%20At%20BRICS%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20economic%20reforms%20and%20the%20technological%20leap%20undertaken%20by%20India%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20India%20will%20emerge%20as%20the%20growth%20engine%20of%20the%20world%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20BRICS%20Business%20Forum%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20PM%20further%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20resolved%20to%20turn%20India%20into%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20congratulated%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Council%20on%20its%20tenth%20anniversary%20and%20said%20that%20BRICS%20Business%20Council%20has%20played%20a%20very%20vital%20role%20in%20enhancing%20our%20economic%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20many%20congratulations%20and%20best%20wishes%20to%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Council%20on%20its%20tenth%20anniversary.%20In%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Council%20has%20played%20a%20very%20vital%20role%20in%20enhancing%20our%20economic%20cooperation.%20When%20the%20first%20BRICS%20summit%20was%20held%20in%202009%2C%20the%20world%20was%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20massive%20financial%20crisis.%20At%20that%20time%20BRICS%20emerged%20as%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20global%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20time%20also%20amongst%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20tensions%20and%20disputes%20the%20world%20is%20dealing%20with%20e-economic%20challenges.%20In%20such%20times%20once%20again%20the%20role%20of%20BRICS%20countries%20is%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20his%20address%20at%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Forum%20Leaders'%20Dialogue%20in%20Johannesburg%2C%20he%20said%20that%20India%20will%20soon%20be%20a%205%20trillion%20dollar%20economy%20and%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20will%20be%20the%20growth%20engine%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20turmoil%20in%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20India%20today%20is%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20Very%20soon%20India%20will%20become%20a%20five%20trillion%20dollar%20economy.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20doubt%20that%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20India%20will%20be%20the%20growth%20engine%20of%20the%20world%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20that%20India%20has%20converted%20crisis%20and%20difficulties%20into%20opportunities%20for%20economic%20improvements.%20The%20people%20of%20India%20have%20resolve%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20further%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%20we%20have%20carried%20out%20reforms%20and%20mission%20modes%20and%20these%20factors%20have%20helped%20continuously%20improve%20doing%20business%20in%20India.%20We%20have%20also%20reduced%20the%20compliance%20burden%20and%20removed%20red%20tape.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20boost%20in%20investor%20confidence%20due%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20GST%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20insolvency.%20We%20have%20focused%20on%20public%20service%20delivery%20and%20good%20governance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20mentioned%20that%20more%20than%20360%20billion%20dollars%20in%20transfers%20have%20been%20made%20by%20direct%20benefit%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20in%20one%20click%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20India%20get%20direct%20benefit%20transfers.%20This%20has%20increased%20transparency%20in%20service%20delivery%2C%20reduced%20corruption%20and%20middlemen.%20India%20is%20among%20the%20most%20economical%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20cost%20per%20gigabyte%20of%20data.%20Today%20in%20India%20UPI%20is%20used%20at%20all%20levels%20from%20street%20vendors%20to%20large%20shopping%20malls.%20Today%20among%20all%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20is%20the%20country%20with%20the%20highest%20digital%20transaction.%20Countries%20like%20UAE%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20France%20are%20joining%20this%20platform.%20There%20are%20many%20possibilities%20of%20working%20on%20this%20with%20BRICS%20countries%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20scenario%20of%20the%20country%20is%20changing%20due%20to%20large-scale%20investment%20in%20India's%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20year's%20budget%2C%20we%20have%20kept%20a%20provision%20of%20about%20USD%20120%20billion%20for%20infrastructure.%20By%20way%20of%20this%20investment%2C%20we%20are%20laying%20a%20strong%20foundation%20for%20a%20new%20India%20of%20the%20future.%20Rapid%20changes%20are%20coming%20into%20effect%20in%20all%20areas%20of%20rail%2C%20water%2C%20infrastructure%20and%20airways%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20today%2C%20new%20highways%20are%20being%20constructed%20in%20India%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20ten%20thousand%20kilometres%20per%20year.%20The%20number%20of%20airports%20has%20doubled%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20to%20promote%20investment%20and%20production%2C%20we%20have%20implemented%20a%20Production%20Linked%20Incentives%20scheme.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIndia's%20manufacturing%20sector%20is%20becoming%20competitive%20due%20to%20reduction%20in%20logistics%20cost.%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world%20leaders%20in%20the%20field%20of%20Renewable%20Energy.%20We%20are%20making%20active%20steps%20to%20make%20India%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20hub%20in%20areas%20like%20solar%20energy%2C%20wind%20energy%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20green%20ammonia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20this%20will%20create%20a%20big%20market%20for%20renewable%20technology%20in%20India.%20Today%20India%20has%20the%20third-largest%20start-up%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20world.%20There%20are%20currently%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20unicorns%20in%20India%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasizing%20the%20vision%20of%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%2C%20Make%20for%20the%20World%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20that%20in%20sectors%20like%20IT%2C%20Telecom%2C%20FinTech%2C%20AI%20and%20semiconductors%20we%20are%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20efforts%20have%20had%20a%20direct%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20common%20people.%20The%20income%20of%20the%20people%20has%20increased%20almost%20three%20times%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20Business%20Forum.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHighlighting%20the%20role%20of%20women%20in%20all%20sectors%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20economic%20development%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20IT%20to%20Space%2C%20from%20banking%20to%20healthcare%20women%20are%20contributing%20to%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20country%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20with%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20further%20invited%20all%20the%20countries%20to%20be%20part%20of%20India's%20development%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20attendance%20of%20South%20Africa's%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%2C%20Brazil's%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%2C%20and%20India's%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jingping%20was%20notably%20absent%20from%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20foreign%20minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20was%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSoon%20after%20the%20Business%20Forum%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20arrived%20at%20the%20Summer%20Place%20in%20Johannesburg%20to%20