l%20to%20live%20on%20an%20abandoned%20farm%20they%20bought%20for%20%24103%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJohn%20and%20Tara%20Newby%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%2C%20off-grid%20homestead%20where%20they%20could%20raise%20their%20sons.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey've%20turned%20their%20renovation%20journey%20into%20a%20YouTube%20career%20that%20lets%20them%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20their%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20John%20and%20Tara%20Newby%2C%20moving%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Portugal%20was%20a%20happy%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20short%20holiday%20in%20Portugal%20during%20the%20pandemic%20turned%20into%20a%20month-long%20stay%20because%20of%20a%20change%20in%20travel%20rules%20that%20prevented%20them%20from%20going%20home%20without%20quarantining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20the%20extra%20time%20on%20their%20hands%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20this%20would%20be%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20look%20for%20a%20house%20to%20buy%20in%20the%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20abandoned%20farm%20that%20they%20bought%20in%20Portugal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc45144ef9f30019f7ba49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Portugal%20to%20restore%20and%20live%20on%20an%20abandoned%20farm.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20looking%20at%20a%20lifestyle%20that%20would%20mean%20we%20could%20get%20out%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20spend%20more%20time%20outside%2C%20have%20a%20better%20climate%2C%20and%20space%20for%20our%20children%20to%20grow%20a%20bit%20more%20wild%20and%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20Tara%2C%2035%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20already%20knew%20what%20they%20wanted%3A%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20that%20they%20could%20turn%20into%20a%20homestead%20with%20a%20house%20that%20they%20could%20fix%20up%20with%20their%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20couple%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20second%20property%20they%20viewed%20%E2%80%94%20an%20abandoned%20farm%20set%20on%20three%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20walked%20through%20the%20gates%2C%20and%20John's%20amazing%20at%20seeing%20potential%20when%20other%20people%20don't%20%E2%80%94%20me%20included%2C%26quot%3B%20Tara%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20think%20we%20could%20make%20this%20work.'%20And%20that%20was%20it%20really.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20abandoned%20farm%20and%20the%20buildings%20that%20sit%20on%20the%20land.%20The%20main%20house%20and%20a%20second%20building%20is%20visible%2C%20while%20a%20third%2C%20shorter%20building%20is%20hidden%20by%20the%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e2e68fbd98a600197a7578%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20abandoned%20farm%20that%20the%20Newbys%20bought%20in%20Portugal.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20is%20located%20just%20outside%20of%20a%20small%20town%20called%20Amarante%20%E2%80%94%20about%20220%20miles%20north%20of%20Lisbon%20%E2%80%94%20in%20northern%20Portugal%2C%20and%20it%20came%20with%20three%20small%20stone%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20living%20and%20traveling%20around%20in%20a%20van%20at%20that%20time%20%E2%80%94%20bought%20the%20farm%20for%2095%2C000%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%24103%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20took%20them%20a%20long%20time%20to%20decide%20what%20they%20were%20going%20to%20do%20with%20the%20property.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20idea%20was%20a%20lifestyle%20business%20or%20a%20holiday%20home.%20We%20also%20thought%20about%20moving%20permanently%2C%20and%20when%20we%20came%20back%20out%20here%2C%20we%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it%20more%20and%20more%20the%20longer%20we%20spent%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Tara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20they%20decided%20they%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%2C%20off-grid%20homestead%20where%20they%20could%20raise%20their%20children.%20At%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20already%20had%20their%20first%20son%20Crusoe%2C%20and%20Tara%20was%20pregnant%20with%20their%20second%20child%2C%20Sawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%2C%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20their%20two%20children%20posing%20for%20a%20family%20selfie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc45085e5d5a00195ee075%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22951%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20turn%20the%20abandoned%20farm%20into%20a%20sustainable%2C%20off-grid%20homestead%20for%20their%20family.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20a%20life%20where%20they%20would%20have%20enough%20space%20to%20be%20outside%20a%20lot%20to%20explore%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20there%20was%20also%20a%20financial%20aspect%20in%20their%20decision%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20property.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20sold%20their%20house%20in%20England%20when%20they%20became%20van-lifers%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrices%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20in%20Bristol%20had%20been%20going%20quite%20crazy%2C%20so%20we%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20equity%20in%20that%20property%20that's%20enough%20to%20buy%20the%20farm%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20John%2C%2045%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222109%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20main%20house%20building%20before%20renovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df2daeb698ac0019dc0c0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221581%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20main%20house%20building%20before%20renovation.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20money%20was%20in%20a%20bank%20account%2C%20and%20the%20interest%20rates%20were%20low%20back%20then%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20doing%20anything%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20came%20to%20Portugal%20and%20we%20thought%2C%20well%2C%20why%20not%20just%20buy%20a%20house%20here%20with%20the%20money%20that%20we've%20got%20in%20the%20bank%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20process%20of%20buying%20a%20home%20in%20Portugal%20is%20fairly%20straightforward%2C%20John%20says.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20employed%20a%20solicitor%20to%20assist%20them%20with%20the%20legal%20aspect%20of%20things%20and%20also%20to%20check%20that%20the%20property%20had%20all%20of%20the%20certifications%20required%20for%20renovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20Portugal's%20got%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20laws%20to%20do%20with%20the%20planning%20commission%2C%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20you%20can%20update%20properties%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20of%20the%20buildings%20on%20the%20farm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc76615e5d5a00195eecde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20buildings%20on%20the%20farm%20had%20fallen%20into%20disrepair%20and%20were%20overrun%20with%20plants.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20many%20abandoned%20properties%20available%20for%20sale%20in%20the%20country%2C%20not%20all%20of%20them%20have%20the%20necessary%20paperwork%20required%20for%20buyers%20to%20apply%20for%20habitation%20or%20renovation%20permits%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProperty%20buyers%20also%20need%20a%20taxpayer%20identification%20number%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feportugal.gov.pt%2Fen%2Fservicos%2Fpedir-o-numero-de-identificacao-fiscal-para-pessoa-singular%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520taxpayer%2520identification%2520number%2520or%2C%252C%2520opening%2520bank%2520accounts%252C%2520etc.%5C%22%3ENIF%20number%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20before%20they%20can%20enter%20a%20contract%2C%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20can%20prove%20where%20your%20finances%20come%20from%2C%20so%20that%20there%20are%20no%20money%20laundering%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20to%20the%20farm%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlthough%20no%20one%20had%20lived%20on%20the%20property%20for%20over%2020%20years%2C%20everything%20looked%20like%20it%20had%20been%20left%20the%20way%20it%20was%20on%20the%20day%20the%20farm%20was%20abandoned.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222102%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20previous%20owners%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20furniture%20and%20items%20behind.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df2dbfb698ac0019dc0c4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221577%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20room%20inside%20one%20of%20the%20smaller%20buildings%20on%20the%20farm.%20It's%20full%20of%20items%20and%20furniture%20that%20the%20previous%20owners%20left%20behind.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Newbys%20moved%20in%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20had%20to%20do%20was%20clear%20out%20all%20the%20items%20that%20the%20previous%20occupants%20had%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20literally%20looked%20like%20someone%20had%20walked%20out%20the%20door%20on%20your%20average%20Tuesday%20and%20just%20never%20came%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Tara%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20biscuits%20in%20the%20cupboards%2C%20there%20were%20clothes%20in%20the%20cupboards%2C%20the%20beds%20were%20made%20up.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cobwebs%20and%20dust%20covered%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20rooms%20inside%20the%20three%20buildings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df2db5bd98a6001978da15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221578%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECobwebs%20and%20dust%20covered%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20rooms%20inside%20the%20three%20buildings.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20they%20spent%20about%2010%20days%20emptying%20all%20the%20rooms%20and%20giving%20the%20space%20a%20good%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20to%20clear%20out%2C%20a%20lot%20to%20sort%20through.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20spiderwebs%20and%20dust%20covering%20every%20surface%20of%20the%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOnce%20the%20cleaning%20was%20done%2C%20the%20couple%20moved%20on%20to%20clearing%20the%20land%20so%20that%20they%20could%20start%20growing%20their%20own%20fruit%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20tiny%20house%20before%20renovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db1d571f51cc00196995f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20one%20of%20the%20buildings%20on%20the%20farm%20before%20renovation.%20The%20couple%20ended%20up%20turning%20this%20shed%20into%20a%20tiny%20guest%20home%20and%20office.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20nature%20had%20completely%20taken%20over%20large%20sections%20of%20their%20property%2C%20hiding%20outdoor%20stone%20tables%20and%20old%20staircases%20that%20the%20couple%20didn't%20even%20know%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20t