0renovation.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETara%20gave%20birth%20to%20Sawyer%20in%20September%202022%2C%20and%20the%20family%20of%20four%20returned%20to%20Portugal%20just%20a%20month%20later.%20They've%20been%20at%20the%20property%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20they%20returned%2C%20the%20couple%20ramped%20up%20their%20renovation%20progress%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20house%20started%20to%20take%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22766%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20during%20renovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db1e091f51cc001969961b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20during%20renovation.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20main%20house%2C%20the%20couple%20turned%20the%20first%20floor%20into%20a%20cozy%2C%20open-plan%20living%20room%20and%20kitchen%20space.%20Upstairs%2C%20the%20four%20of%20them%20sleep%20together%20in%20a%20single%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20furniture%20and%20decor%20they%20have%20in%20their%20house%20is%20made%20from%20upcycled%20items%2C%20including%20a%20wooden%20table%20that%20John%20crafted%20from%20an%20old%20wine%20press%20they%20found%20on%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20of%20the%20couple's%20goals%20is%20to%20live%20a%20self-sufficient%20and%20sustainable%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20that%20includes%20going%20off-grid%20and%20growing%20their%20own%20food.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22765%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20after%20renovation.%20The%20space%20has%20been%20transformed%20into%20a%20cozy%20living%20room%20and%20open-concept%20kitchen%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db1df45e5d5a00195e1524%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20floor%20of%20their%20home%20has%20been%20transformed%20into%20a%20cozy%20living%20room%20and%20open%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20an%20off-grid%20water%20system%20as%20well%20as%20freshwater%20flowing%20into%20their%20property%20from%20a%20stream.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20farm%20draws%20electricity%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20the%20family%20does%20rely%20on%20solar%20energy%20as%20well.%20They%20are%20still%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20evaluating%20whether%20they%20should%20take%20their%20electricity%20completely%20off-grid%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPortugal%20actually%20has%20got%20really%20good%20renewable%20energy%20as%20part%20of%20the%20national%20grid.%20I%20think%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20this%20year%2C%20a%20hundred%20percent%20of%20the%20electricity%20of%20the%20country%20has%20been%20supplied%20entirely%20by%20renewables%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20couple's%20sons%2C%20Crusoe%2C%20standing%20next%20to%20a%20solar%20power%20setup.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e30deab698ac0019ddc9c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20couple's%20sons%2C%20Crusoe%2C%20standing%20next%20to%20a%20solar%20power%20setup.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%C2%A0That%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20also%20means%20that%20electricity%20prices%20in%20the%20country%20are%20generally%20pretty%20good%2C%20he%20said.%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20weighing%20that%20opportunity%20cost%20of%20whether%20it's%20important%20for%20us%20to%20go%20completely%20off-grid%20individually%2C%20or%20whether%20the%20Portuguese%20government's%20doing%20a%20good%20enough%20job%20with%20the%20renewables%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Newbys%20have%20been%20documenting%20every%20step%20of%20their%20Portuguese%20farm%20renovation%20on%20their%20YouTube%20channel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc79545e5d5a00195eeded%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40TheNewbys%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20back%20in%202020%20when%20they%20were%20still%20living%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20way%20for%20them%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20family%20members%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20a%20hobby%20at%20first.%20We%20started%20off%20by%20posting%20a%20couple%20of%20videos%20for%20Tara's%20parents%2C%20who%20were%20in%20Zimbabwe%2C%20to%20kind%20of%20keep%20them%20in%20the%20loop%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20pandemic%2C%20John%20and%20Tara%20had%20been%20working%20together%20at%20a%20travel%20agency%20and%20had%20a%20few%20exciting%20trips%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWork%20was%20going%20to%20take%20us%20to%20Tanzania%20to%20see%20some%20chimpanzees.%20Then%20we%20were%20off%20to%20Antarctica%20to%20get%20married%2C%20and%20we%20were%20going%20to%20do%20some%20other%20bits%20of%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20thought%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20We%20should%20just%20start%20filming%20it%20and%20putting%20together%20these%20compilations%20of%20travel%20videos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bedroom%20is%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20main%20house.%20The%20entire%20family%20sleeps%20in%20the%20same%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc7ac04ef9f30019f7c854%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entire%20family%20shares%20one%20bedroom%20in%20the%20main%20home.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20it%20happened%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20ended%20up%20quitting%20their%20jobs%20to%20travel%20around%20Europe%20in%20a%20van%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20filmed%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20road%2C%20and%20when%20they%20finally%20settled%20down%20on%20the%20Portuguese%20farm%2C%20they%20filmed%20that%20process%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20now%2C%20creating%20content%20for%20their%20YouTube%20channel%20has%20become%20their%20full-time%20job%20%E2%80%94%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20parents%20and%20renovating%20the%20home.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20renovated%20tiny%20house%20is%20now%20an%20office%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db1d351f51cc00196995ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovated%20tiny%20house%20is%20now%20an%20office%20space.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20essentially%20have%20three%20full-time%20jobs.%20We%20are%20full-time%20parents%2C%20our%20kids%20don't%20go%20to%20nursery%20or%20anything.%20Then%20we%20have%20our%20full-time%20YouTube%20business%2C%20making%20content.%20And%20we%20are%20full-time%20renovators%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20homestead%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Tara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20they%20love%20this%20lifestyle%2C%20the%20couple%20admits%20that%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20managing%20their%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20to%20make%20all%20of%20those%20things%20marry%20up%20and%20work%20together%20is%20hard%2C%20especially%20because%20it's%20usually%20dictated%20by%20two%20very%20small%20people%20who%20need%20us%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20couple%20releases%20two%20YouTube%20videos%20every%20week%2C%20and%20each%20video%20takes%20three%20days%20to%20film%20and%20edit.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22766%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bedroom%20area%20in%20the%20main%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db1d631f51cc00196995fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bedroom%20area%20in%20the%20main%20house.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0To%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fyoutube%2Fanswer%2F72857%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3Emonetize%20their%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20had%20to%20have%20a%20thousand%20subscribers%20and%204%2C000%20watch%20hours%2C%20John%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20took%20us%20about%20half%20a%20year%20to%20do%20that%2C%20to%20get%201%2C000%20subscribers.%20And%20then%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20year%2C%20we%20were%20at%20about%207%2C000%20or%208%2C000%20subscribers%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20their%20channel%20has%20over%20144%2C000%20subscribers%2C%20and%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5fOGrWG52hg%5C%22%3Emost%20popular%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20viewed%20over%201.5%20million%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlongside%20that%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we've%20got%20our%20Patreon%20accounts%20so%20we%20need%20to%20service%20that%2C%20and%20we%20are%20also%20working%20to%20get%20brand%20sponsorships%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFor%20those%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20Portugal%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20some%20advice%3A%20Use%20local%20property%20websites%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20written%20in%20Portuguese.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tiny%20house%20doubles%20as%20a%20guest%20room%20and%20a%20home%20office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc79615e5d5a00195eee00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tiny%20house%20doubles%20as%20a%20guest%20room%20and%20a%20home%20office.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20English%20websites%20out%20there%20that%20will%20sometimes%20charge%20a%20premium%20on%20a%20property%20because%20they're%20written%20in%20English%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20couple%20suggests%20browsing%20listings%20on%20local%20real-estate%20websites%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imovirtual.com%2F%5C%22%3EImovirtual%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20local%20Portuguese%20websites%20that%C2%A0Google%20does%20a%20really%20great%20job%20of%20translating%20now.%20So%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20one%20of%20these%20local%20websites%20you'll%20get%20the%20local%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlthough%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20country%20with%20two%20small%20kids%20in%20tow%20can%20be%20a%20daunting%20experience%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20no%20regrets%20about%20their%20decision.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20family%20standing%20outside%20the%20entrance%20of%20their%20main%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e317ceb698ac0019ddd183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20family%20standing%20outside%20the%20entrance%20of%20their%20main%20house.%3Cp%3EThe%20Newbys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20a%20real%20thing%20about%20Portugal%20is%20that%20the%20people%20are%20incredible%20and%20they're%20so%20family-oriented.%20It's%20a%20really%20different%20feel%20from%20the%20UK%20and%20from%20other%20places%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20it's%20something%20that%20we%20really%20love%20about%20being%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Tara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20each%20day%20has%20its%20own%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20a%20renovation%20problem%20or%20the%20stress%20of%20raising%20two%20young%20children%20alone%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20%E2%80%94%20the%20couple%20says%20they're%20glad%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20this%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20that%20we%20had%20expected%20and%20hoped%20for%20is%20happening.%20Like%2C%20it's%20perfect%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20loads%20of%20space%20for%20our%20kids%20to%20grow%2C%20we're%20growing%20our%20own%20food%2C%20we're%20enjoying%20our%20days%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20disappointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-diy-abandoned-farm-portugal-off-grid-youtube-creator-family-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692749641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e317ceb698ac0019ddd183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-diy-abandoned-farm-portugal-off-grid-youtube-creator-family-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20loads%20of%20space%20for%20our%20kids%20to%20grow%2C%20we're%20growing%20our%20own%20food%2C%20we're%20enjoying%20our%20days%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20disappointment%2C%26quot%3B%20Newby%20told%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-diy-abandoned-farm-portugal-off-grid-youtube-creator-family-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20energy%20minister%20announces%20%24245m%20for%20Ukraine%20nuclear%20fuel%20purchases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692749536000%2C%22visual%22