22title%22%3A%22Number%20Of%20US%20Children%20Killed%20By%20Guns%20Hit%20Record%20High%20In%202021%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChild%20gun%20deaths%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20hit%20a%20record%20high%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20published%20by%20the%20American%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention's%20mortality%20database%2C%20the%20study%20published%20on%20Monday%20in%20the%20AAP's%20journal%20Pediatrics%20found%20that%204%2C752%20children%20died%20from%20gun-related%20injuries%20in%202021%2C%20the%20latest%20year%20for%20which%20data%20was%20available%2C%20up%20from%204%2C368%20in%202020%20and%203%2C390%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGun%20violence%20has%20been%20the%20number%20one%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20children%20in%20the%20United%20States%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20was%20published%20as%20Tennessee%20lawmakers%20opened%20a%20special%20session%20on%20public%20safety%20after%20a%20Nashville%20school%20shooting%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20killed%20three%20children%20and%20three%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnie%20Andrews%2C%20a%20South%20Carolina%20pediatrician%20and%20gun%20violence%20prevention%20researcher%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20study%2C%20said%20that%20when%20she%20became%20a%20doctor%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20take%20care%20of%20so%20many%20children%20with%20bullet%20holes%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%2C%20in%20every%20children's%20hospital%20across%20this%20country%2C%20there%20are%20children%20in%20the%20pediatric%20intensive%20care%20units%20suffering%20from%20firearm%20injuries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20further%20showed%20that%20Black%20children%20accounted%20for%20around%2067%25%20of%20firearm%20homicides%20while%20white%20children%20made%20up%20about%2078%25%20of%20gun-assisted%20suicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIman%20Omer%2C%20a%20junior%20at%20Vanderbilt%20University%20in%20Nashville%20and%20an%20anti-gun%20violence%20advocate%20with%20Students%20Demand%20Action%2C%20said%20the%20study's%20findings%20were%20devastating%20but%20unsurprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20year%2C%20I%20know%20that%20128%20children%20and%20teens%20in%20Tennessee%20die%20by%20guns%2C%26quot%3B%20Omer%20said%20as%20she%20headed%20to%20the%20state's%20capitol%20Tuesday%20to%20join%20protesters%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20tougher%20gun%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETennessee%20Governor%20Bill%20Lee%2C%20who%20knew%20two%20of%20the%20teachers%20killed%20in%20the%20Nashville%20shooting%2C%20had%20asked%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20special%20session%20to%20bolster%20so%20called%20red%20flag%20laws%20aimed%20at%20keeping%20firearms%20out%20of%20the%20hands%20of%20people%20deemed%20to%20be%20a%20threat.%20He%20has%20faced%20resistance%20from%20his%20fellow%20Republicans%2C%20who%20control%20the%20statehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Tennessee%20Firearms%20Association%20expressed%20concern%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20some%20Republican%20legislators%20have%20said%20that%20no%20Red%20Flag%20laws%20will%20pass%2C%20far%20fewer%20have%20stated%20that%20no%20laws%20that%20would%20have%20any%20negative%20impact%20on%202nd%20Amendment%20protected%20rights%20would%20pass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692741300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fqn6uc1s8_gun-violence_625x300_21_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnumber-of-us-children-killed-by-guns-hit-record-high-in-2021-report-4320823%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Child%20gun%20deaths%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20hit%20a%20r