ption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20lot%2C%20however%2C%20was%20owned%20by%20US%20Bank%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inquirer.com%2Fnews%2Fphiladelphia-community-garden-tax-lien-us-bank-gentrification-20211006.html%23loaded%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebecause%20of%20a%20failed%20property%20deal%20with%20the%20city%20of%20Philadelphia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20dating%20to%201997.%20Thousands%20of%20properties%20tied%20up%20in%20the%20deal%20sat%20neglected%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20locals%20transformed%20some%20into%20urban%20gardens.%20But%20as%20the%20city%20gentrified%2C%20these%20lots%20became%20more%20valuable%20and%20drew%20the%20interest%20of%20real-estate%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%2C%20a%20board%20member%20of%20Neighborhood%20Gardens%20Trust%2C%20is%20part%20of%20a%20coalition%20of%20urban%20growers%2C%20advocacy%20groups%2C%20and%20local%20officials%20in%20Philadelphia%20trying%20to%20protect%20and%20expand%20the%20city's%20450%20urban%20gardens%20and%20farms.%20There%20is%20growing%20evidence%20that%20these%20spaces%20not%20only%20improve%20food%20security%20in%20many%20Black%20and%20brown%20neighborhoods%20but%20also%20reduce%20violence%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fheatislands%2Fclimate-change-and-heat-islands%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20%26quot%3Burban%20heat%20island%26quot%3B%20effect%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20in%20Philadelphia%20is%20that%20gardens%20are%20not%20seen%20as%20permanent%20use%20but%20temporary%2C%26quot%3B%20Ash%20Richards%2C%20who%20in%202019%20became%20the%20first%20urban-agriculture%20director%20at%20Philadelphia%20Parks%20%26amp%3B%20Recreation%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BA%20solution%20is%20to%20make%20policies%20that%20provide%20a%20pathway%20to%20preservation%20that%20lowers%20barriers%20to%20access%20and%20ownership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Richards%20collaborated%20with%20a%20grassroots%20coalition%20of%20Black%20and%20brown%20growers%20called%20Soil%20Generation%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.phila.gov%2Fmedia%2F20230421153052%2FPhiladelphia-Urban-Agriculture-Plan.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eto%20come%20up%20with%20the%20city's%20first-ever%20plan%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20urban%20agriculture.%20The%20plan%2C%20named%20%26quot%3BGrowing%20from%20the%20Root%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20finalized%20in%20April%20and%20includes%20nearly%2090%20recommendations%20for%20the%20city%20government%20to%20secure%20and%20support%20community%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20urban-agriculture%20office%20has%20a%20%24290%2C000%20budget%20this%20fiscal%20year%2C%C2%A0Richards%2C%20who%20hopes%20to%20increase%20funding%20in%20future%20years%2C%20said.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20priorities%20is%20establishing%20a%20resource%20center%20that%20provides%20training%20for%20growers%20and%20offers%20seeds%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20tools%20needed%20for%20gardens%2C%20Richards%20added.%20The%20office%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20growers%20to%20apply%20online%20to%20lease%20land%20owned%20by%20the%20parks%20department%2C%20and%20it's%20translating%20the%20application%20into%20five%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221703%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20at%20a%20community%20garden%20in%20Philadelphia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e3fd82b698ac0019dea8bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221703%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20portion%20of%20Five%20Loaves%20Two%20Fish%20was%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20sold%20off.%3Cp%3EFive%20Loaves%20Two%20Fish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20changes%20must%20go%20beyond%20Philadelphia%20Parks%20%26amp%3B%20Recreation%2C%20Richards%20said.%20Ensuring%20urban%20gardens%20aren't%20sold%20out%20from%20under%20growers%20who%20don't%20own%20the%20land%20%E2%80%94%20yet%20have%20been%20tending%20to%20it%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20requires%20additional%20actions%20by%20the%20City%20Council%20and%20other%20agencies.%20That%20includes%20Philadelphia's%20Land%20Bank%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20in%202014%20to%20revitalize%20both%20public%20and%20private%20property%20left%20vacant%20or%20underused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20budget%20my%20office%20received%20is%20a%20start%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20work%20is%20funded%20and%20staffed%2C%26quot%3B%20Richards%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20rely%20on%20people%20volunteering%20their%20time%20for%20the%20next%2010%20years%20to%20get%20this%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImplementing%20the%20urban-agriculture%20plan%20could%20yield%20more%20benefits%20than%20a%20boosted%20supply%20of%20fresh%2C%20local%20food%2C%20Richards%20said.%20Many%20Black%20and%20brown%20neighborhoods%20don't%20have%20enough%20green%20spaces%2C%20which%20makes%20residents%20more%20susceptible%20to%20extreme%20heat.%20Gardens%20can%20help%20keep%20people%20cool%20and%20improve%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20Greenberg%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Neighborhood%20Gardens%20Trust%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.1718503115%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eresearch%20had%20found%20that%20green%20spaces%20in%20Philadelphia%20reduced%20gun%20violence%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2688343%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efeelings%20of%20depression%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20empirical%20evidence%20has%20made%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20being%20able%20to%20make%20the%20case%20that%20urban%20agriculture%20has%20economic%20benefits%2C%20as%20well%20as%20social%20and%20health%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20Greenberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20there's%20the%20more-intuitive%20knowledge%20that%20these%20places%20build%20community%20and%20strengthen%20people's%20sense%20of%20connection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20gather%20at%20a%20community%20garden%20in%20Philadelphia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e3fe20b698ac0019dea8c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20garden%20is%20a%20place%20where%20people%20can%20commune%2C%20and%20it%20keeps%20negativity%20down%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%26quot%3B%20Young%20said.%3Cp%3EFive%20Loaves%20Two%20Fish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20kind%20of%20connection%20is%20what%20Young%20set%20out%20to%20achieve%20at%20Five%20Loaves%20Two%20Fish%20with%20his%20cofounder%2C%20Beverly%20Giles%20Carter.%20They%20just%20held%20a%20going-away%20party%20for%20local%20high-school%20graduates%20who%20had%20worked%20at%20the%20garden%20for%20years%2C%20Young%20said.%20Now%20that%20the%20site%20is%20secured%2C%20they%20want%20to%20set%20up%20a%20larger%20program%20for%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20growing%20food%20and%20building%20connections%20with%20the%20young%20and%20the%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Young%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20garden%20is%20a%20place%20where%20people%20can%20commune%2C%20and%20it%20keeps%20negativity%20down%20in%20the%20neighborhood.%20So%20it's%20served%20its%20purpose%20as%20a%20place%20to%20feed%20people%2C%20rest%2C%20and%20communicate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furban-community-gardens-philadelphia-land-development-protection-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692738796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22