.%20%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20time%20with%20the%20Aska%20gave%20me%20some%20hope%20for%20our%20science-fiction%20future%2C%20it%20also%20left%20me%20disheartened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplinsky%20told%20me%20that%20hopping%20over%20traffic%20in%20a%20flying%20car%20isn't%20realistic%20%E2%80%94%20with%20our%20current%20understanding%20of%20physics%2C%20anyway.%20As%20long%20as%20flight%20requires%20pushing%20massive%20amounts%20of%20air%2C%20taking%20off%20so%20close%20to%20other%20cars%20would%20be%20too%20dangerous.%20You'd%20need%20some%20kind%20of%20silent%2C%20UFO-like%20propulsion%20system%20to%20make%20it%20work%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20to%20anyone%20who's%20shared%20my%20boredom-induced%20daydreams%20behind%20the%20wheel%3A%20Keep%20dreaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faska-a5-flying-car-evtol-test-ride-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692732977000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e4ea1abd98a600197c13e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faska-a5-flying-car-evtol-test-ride-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Say%20goodbye%20to%20rush-hour%20traffic.%20This%20flying%20car%20will%20cruise%20at%20150%20mph%20when%20it%20goes%20on%20sale%20in%202026.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tlevin%40insider.com%20(Tim%20Levin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A155%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faska-a5-flying-car-evtol-test-ride-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vikram%20all%20set%20for%20soft%20landing%20as%20India%20reaches%20for%20the%20Moon%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692732823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102956556%2Cimgsize-2695669.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%2