3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20Central%20agencies%20over%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20raids%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Trinamool%20alleges%20that%20central%20agencies%20are%20acting%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20home%20is%20facing%20torture%20every%20day.%20Yesterday%20also%20all%20night.%20No%20one%20told%20me.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20of%20it%20from%20the%20lawyer.%20There%20was%20no%20intimation.%20The%20boy%20(Abhishek%20Banerjee)%20got%20back%20only%20day%20before%20yesterday.%20Suddenly%20they%20arrived%20at%20four%2C%20five%20places.%20I%20got%20news%20that%20they%20left%20at%20six%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20raids%20that%20took%20place%20on%20at%20least%20three%20locations%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20speaking%20at%20the%20annual%20meeting%20of%20government%20officials%2C%20puja%20committees%20and%20police%20officers%20ahead%20of%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20celebrations%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20critics%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20Central%20government%2C%20has%20always%20backed%20Opposition%20leaders%20facing%20investigation%20by%20Central%20agencies.%20Earlier%20she%20even%20said%20the%20use%20of%20Central%20agencies%20against%20Opposition%20will%20not%20help%20the%20BJP%20get%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20nephew%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20and%20members%20of%20his%20family%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20Central%20agencies%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20coal%20smuggling%20scam.%C2%A0%20He%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20someone%20comes%20to%20my%20home.%20Or%20I%20send%20police%20to%20your%20home.%20What%20does%20the%20law%20say%3F%20They%20should%20have%20a%20warrant.%20They%20will%20inform%20the%20people%20at%20home%20as%20to%20why%20they%20have%20come.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20raid%2C%20other%20people%20will%20also%20be%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20central%20agencies%20of%20illegal%20activities%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20breaking%20locks%20and%20entering.%20There%20is%20no%20information.%C2%A0%20In%20some%20places%20they%20are%20breaking%20locks%20and%20entering.%C2%A0%20If%20someone%20is%20not%20at%20home%20and%20the%20home%20is%20closed%E2%80%A6%20Even%20if%20someone%20is%20there%20to%20make%20tea%2C%20they%20are%20throwing%20them%20out%20of%20the%20home.%20After%20entering%20there%20are%20no%20witnesses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20security%20aspect%20of%20such%20visits.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20there%20be%20a%20guarantee%20that%20you%20are%20not%20planting%20any%20explosives%E2%80%A6%20That%20you%20are%20not%20planting%20a%20gun%20at%20the%20home%E2%80%A6%20That%20you%20are%20not%20carrying%20crores%20of%20rupees%20in%20a%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20Centre%20of%20%26quot%3Billegal%20political%20vendetta%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20run%20the%20country%20like%20this.%C2%A0%20We%20are%20citizens%20of%20an%20independent%20country.%20The%20PM%20boasts%20when%20he%20is%20abroad%20that%20he%20takes%20everyone%20along.%20And%20look%20at%20the%20Opposition-ruled%20states.%20They%20are%20biting%20us%20like%20ants.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20searched%20offices%20of%20Leaps%20and%20Bounds%20Private%20Limited%20in%20New%20Alipore%2C%20Joka%20and%20Thakurpukur%20on%20Monday%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20probe%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20appointments%20in%20government-run%20and%20government-aided%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%