%20and%20China%20pushing%20for%20an%20expansion%20of%20BRICS%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20dozens%20of%20other%20countries%20from%20Ethiopia%20to%20Indonesia%20and%20Iran%20will%20also%20be%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20outreach%20sessions%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussian%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EPresident%20Vladimir%20Putin%20cancelled%20his%20trip%20primarily%20to%20prevent%20South%20Africa%20from%20grappling%20with%20the%20predicament%20of%20executing%20his%20arrest%20warrant%20issued%20by%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%20India%20and%20Brazil%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmg.co.za%2Fpolitics%2F2023-08-22-india-china-expected-to-thrash-out-border-disputes-on-sidelines-of-brics-summit%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erejected%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20proposal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20relocate%20the%20summit%20to%20China%20in%20order%20to%20circumvent%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20airport%2C%20Modi%20was%20greeted%20by%20South%20African%20vice%20president%20Paul%20Mashatile.%20Since%20the%20Chinese%20president%E2%80%99s%20sojourn%20was%20also%20a%20state%20visit%2C%20President%20Ramaphosa%20himself%20welcomed%20Xi%20at%20the%20steps%20of%20his%20official%20plane.%20The%20South%20African%20foreign%20minister%20Naledi%20Pandor%20officiated%20at%20the%20welcome%20ceremony%20for%20the%20Brazilian%20president.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20this%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20would%20be%20in%20the%20same%20multilateral%20event%20since%20last%20November%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20speculation%20that%20both%20countries%20were%20creating%20positive%20atmospherics%20to%20allow%20the%20two%20leaders%20to%20meet%20in%20South%20Africa.%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20visit%20Delhi%20for%20the%20G-20%20summit%20next%20month%2C%20but%20that%20may%20only%20be%20a%20quick%20trip.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Xi%20skipped%20the%20business%20forum%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%20with%20China%E2%80%99s%20commerce%20minister%20Wang%20Wentao%20delivering%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20clarity%20on%20why%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20BRICS%20business%20forum.%20He%20took%20part%20in%20formal%20talks%20and%20attended%20a%20lunch%20hosted%20by%20President%20Ramaphosa%20before%20this%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20met%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20nearly%20a%20year%20since%20Bali%20at%20the%20G-20%20Leaders%20Retreat.%20However%2C%20no%20photo%20has%20emerged%20so%20far%20of%20both%20of%20them%20conversing%20as%20they%20did%20at%20the%20G-20%20summit%20in%202022.%20It%20took%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feight-months-later-india-says-modi-xi-did-talk-about-stabilising-ties-at-bali-encounter%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20eight%20months%20for%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20admit%20that%20more%20than%20pleasantries%20had%20been%20exchanged%20between%20Modi%20and%20Xi%2C%20whose%20armies%20are%20still%20in%20a%20three-year-old%20standoff%20in%20the%20western%20sector%20of%20their%20mountainous%20boundary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20still%20not%20stated%20if%20there%20was%20any%20exchange%20of%20remarks%20at%20the%20BRICS%20dinner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20of%20them%20will%20be%20together%20for%20a%20series%20of%20summit%20events%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20with%20the%20plenary%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20an%20outreach%20session%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20officials%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnarendra-modi-xi-jinping-india-china-south-africa%5C%22%3Eremained%20tight-lipped%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20between%20Modi%20and%20Xi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20BRICS%20business%20forum%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20had%20taught%20the%20lesson%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20having%20%E2%80%9Cresilient%20and%20inclusive%20supply%20chains%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20to%20achieve%20this%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmutual%20trust%20and%20transparency%E2%80%9D%20are%20very%20important.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20they%20could%20pool%20their%20economic%20strengths%20to%20help%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHighlighting%20policy%20concepts%20like%20start-up%20ecosystems%20and%20digital%20payments%2C%20Modi%20invited%20the%20businessmen%20who%20were%20present%20at%20the%20forum%20to%20take%20part%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20journey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20will%20be%20the%20growth%20engine%20of%20the%20world.%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%20India%20turned%20calamity%20and%20tough%20times%20into%20economic%20reforms.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20in%20India%20has%20improved%20due%20to%20the%20work%20done%20in%20the%20mission%20mode%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country%20will%20%E2%80%9Csoon%E2%80%9D%20be%20a%20%245%20trillion%20economy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPutin%20speaks%20about%20de-dollarisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnable%20to%20attend%20the%20summit%20in%20person%2C%20Putin%20delivered%20a%20recorded%20video%20message%2C%20during%20which%20he%20indicated%20that%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20meeting%20would%20be%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20West-centred%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20summit%20would%20discuss%20the%20use%20of%20national%20currencies%20for%20trade%20between%20BRICS%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20objective%2C%20irreversible%20process%20of%20de-dollarisation%20of%20our%20economic%20ties%20is%20gaining%20momentum.%20Efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20work%20out%20effective%20mechanisms%20of%20mutual%20settlements%20and%20financial%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20also%20claimed%20the%20share%20of%20the%20dollar%20in%20trade%20within%20BRICS%20countries%20was%20already%20decreasing%2C%20amounting%20to%20only%2028.7%25%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPutin%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frussia-pulls-out-of-ukraine-grain-deal-heres-what-this-means%5C%22%3EBlack%20Sea%20grain%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20blaming%20the%20West%20for%20not%20implementing%20the%20condition%20of%20selling%20Ukrainian%20wheat%20mostly%20to%20developing%20countries%20impacted%20by%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20BRICS%20will%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20Putin%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cooperate%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20equality%2C%20mutual%20support%20and%20respect%20for%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20interests.%20This%20is%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20future-oriented%20strategic%20course%20of%20our%20association%2C%20a%20course%20that%20meets%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20main%20part%20of%20the%20world%20community%2C%20the%20so-called%C2%A0global%20majority%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20rising%20concern%20in%20Western%20capitals%20that%20BRICS%20would%20be%20expanded%20to%20become%20an%20anti-West%20bloc%2C%20Brazilian%20President%20Lula%20said%20in%20South%20Africa%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20such%20apprehension.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20counterpoint%20to%20the%20G7%2C%20G20%20or%20the%20United%20States%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20s