2C%201957%20and%20the%20term%20of%20the%20state's%20constituent%20assembly%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJha%2C%20who%20has%20challenged%20the%20August%205%2C%202019%20decision%20of%20the%20Centre%20to%20abrogate%20Article%20370%2C%20raised%20the%20legal%20question%20about%20whether%20Article%20370%20ceased%20to%20operate%20or%20exist%20after%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20constituent%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20the%20bench%20to%20raise%20queries%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20submissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Surya%20Kant%20told%20Dwivedi%20that%20the%20court%20has%20to%20look%20at%20the%20Indian%20constituent%20assembly%20debates%20and%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20in%20a%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Article%20370%20was%20framed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20arguing%20somewhat%20differently%20from%20what%20my%20friends%20have%20argued.%20They%20want%20some%20part%20of%20Article%20370%20to%20survive.%20My%20argument%20is%20that%20nothing%20survives.%20All%20the%20powers%20conferred%20under%20Article%20370%2C%20I%20would%20show%2C%20cease%20to%20operate%20once%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20enacted%2C%26quot%3B%20Dwivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20the%20consequence%20of%20the%20argument%20will%20be%20that%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20its%20application%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20would%20%26quot%3Bstand%20frozen%20as%20of%20January%2026%2C%201957%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20no%20further%20development%20in%20Indian%20constitutional%20law%20can%20at%20all%20apply%2C%20according%20to%20you%2C%20to%20the%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20after%201957.%20How%20can%20that%20be%20acceptable%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20told%20Dwivedi%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20asking%20us%20to%20read%20what%20is%20not%20there%20in%20Article%20370.%20Your%20submission%20is%20that%20it%20will%20be%20frozen%20after%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20of%20J-K%20frames%20the%20Constitution%20but%20that%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20following.%20We%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20debates%20in%20a%20manner%20in%20which%20Article%20370%20was%20framed.%26quot%3B%20Dwivedi%20said%20when%20the%20Article%20was%20framed%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20in%20turmoil%20and%20the%20only%20legal%20entity%20was%20the%20state%20government%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20the%20provision%20said%20there%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bconsultation%20and%20concurrence%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20matters%20related%20to%20Union%20and%20concurrent%20list%20and%20those%20which%20do%20not%20fall%20under%20the%20Instrument%20of%20Accession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20constituent%20assembly%20was%20about%20to%20be%20set%20up.%20Hence%2C%20all%20the%20decisions%20which%20were%20taken%20in%20consultation%20and%20concurrence%20with%20the%20state%20government%20were%20to%20be%20placed%20before%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20of%20J-K.%20Therefore%2C%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20temporary%20provision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20lawyer%20said%20looking%20at%20the%20provision%20and%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20debates%2C%20it%20can%20be%20clearly%20inferred%20that%20Article%20370%20was%20temporary%20and%20ceased%20to%20exist%20after%20January%2C%201957.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20what%20was%20being%20submitted%20was%20contrary%20to%20arguments%20advanced%20by%20others%20opposed%20to%20the%20abrogation%20as%20they%20said%20that%20the%20provision%20had%20acquired%20permanent%20status%20after%20the%20term%20of%20the%20state's%20constituent%20assembly%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20is%20creating%20a%20problem.%20Perhaps%20our%20thinking%20in%20the%20manner%20which%20we%20have%20been%20tuned%20to%20think%20for%20the%20past%2070%20years%20is%20that%20there%20should%20be%20One%20Nation-One%20Constitution.%20But%20where%20is%20that%20prescribed%3F%20It%20should%20be%20prescribed%20in%20the%20Constitution%20which%20does%20not%20say%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECJI%20Chandrachud%20then%20asked%20can%20the%20court%20say%20that%20a%20speech%20made%20by%20a%20member%20of%20the%20constituent%20assembly%2C%20however%20weighty%2C%20represented%20the%20commitment%20of%20India%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20interpretation%20of%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20CJI%20said.%20Justice%20Kaul%20also%20questioned%20Dwivedi%20on%20his%20line%20of%20argument%20and%20said%20according%20to%20him%2C%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20defunct%20provision%20and%20no%20purpose%20was%20served%20having%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYet%20the%20provision%20continued%20to%20be%20there%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20Constitution%20Orders%20(orders%20applying%20provisions%20of%20Indian%20Constitution%20to%20J-K)%20have%20been%20issued%20pre-1957%20and%20post%201957.%20Yet%20nobody%20thought%20about%20removing%20it.%20The%20association%20of%20people%20with%20Article%20370%20was%20negatory%20and%20hence%20nothing%20survives.%20This%20is%20your%20argument%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kaul%20summed%20up%20Dwivedi's%20contentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDwivedi%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20past%20practices%20would%20not%20justify%20the%20invalidity%20of%20a%20provision%20and%20this%20is%20a%20settled%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%2C%20as%20I%20understand%2C%20is%20that%20however%20long%20a%20past%20practice%20is%20if%20it%20is%20constitutionally%20illegal%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20justified.%20What%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20show%20is%20the%20intent%20of%20our%20Constitution%20framers.%20We%20cannot%20read%20Article%20370%20dehors%20(other%20than)%20the%20intent%20is%20my%20question%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20accept%20that%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20debates%20amount%20to%20an%20assurance%20that%20Article%20370%20would%20dissolve%20itself%20after%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20enacted%20and%20term%20of%20the%20state's%20constituent%20assembly%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20Senior%20advocate%20CU%20Singh%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mohammed%20Yousuf%20Tarigami%20and%20others%20challenged%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%20and%20said%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20could%20not%20be%20divided%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20remained%20inconclusive%20and%20will%20continue%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20abrogation%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20which%20split%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories%20-%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Ladakh%20-%20were%20referred%20to%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692725160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-on-article-370-ceased-to-exist-after-1957-argument-unacceptable-4319997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20Tuesday%20termed%20as%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20the%20submission%20that%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%20ceased%20to%20operate%20once%20the%