0his%20wife%2C%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20after%20ferocious%2C%20wind-whipped%20blazes%20sent%20residents%20jumping%20into%20the%20ocean%20to%20escape%20the%20flames.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20also%20took%20to%20the%20air%20in%20Marine%20One%2C%20the%20presidential%20helicopter%2C%20to%20see%20the%20crushing%20extent%20of%20the%20devastation%20that%20left%20the%20former%20royal%20capital%20in%20ashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20houses%20were%20completely%20destroyed%20by%20the%20wall%20of%20fire%20that%20tore%20through%20the%20town%3B%20the%20shells%20of%20other%20buildings%20still%20stand%2C%20shorn%20of%20the%20vibrancy%20that%20made%20Lahaina%20a%20major%20tourist%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20burned-out%20hulks%20of%20cars%20litter%20roads%20where%20they%20were%20abandoned%20by%20drivers%20who%20realised%20--%20some%20too%20late%20--%20that%20the%20way%20out%20was%20snarled%20with%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692724080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Frpr95gi8_joe-biden-afp_625x300_22_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-compares-maui-wildfires-to-a-small-fire-he-had-in-his-kitchen-in-2004-4320488%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20met%20with%20survivors%20of%20the%20Maui%20wildfires%20in%20Lahaina%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-compares-maui-wildfires-to-a-small-fire-he-had-in-his-kitchen-in-2004-4320488%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-compares-maui-wildfires-to-a-small-fire-he-had-in-his-kitchen-in-2004-4320488%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-compares-maui-wildfires-to-a-small-fire-he-had-in-his-kitchen-in-2004-4320488%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22titl