20so%20too%20has%20that%20of%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkey%20has%20gained%20huge%20visibility%20and%20impact%20in%20foreign%20policy%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20the%20country%20has%20became%20a%20highly%20polarised%20one%20divided%20along%20multiple%20socio-political%20issues%2C%20and%20among%20them%20religion%20is%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20management%20of%20religion%20in%20Turkey%20in%20its%20more%20modern%20form%20did%20not%20start%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%20and%20his%20religious-oriented%20Justice%20and%20Development%20Party%20(AKP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20has%20a%20long%20historical%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReligion%20and%20its%20clashes%20with%20modernity%20are%20nothing%20new.%20The%20use%20of%20religion%20to%20project%20power%20is%20also%20far%20from%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shimmering%20example%20of%20that%20is%20the%20Great%20Hagia%20Sophia.%20Standing%20as%20Christian%20Church%20for%20more%20than%20a%20millennium%2C%20it%20was%20the%20biggest%20in%20the%20world%20for%20centuries%2C%20adorned%20in%20golden%20mosaics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20a%20mosque%20after%20the%20Ottoman%20conquest%20of%20Byzantium%20in%201453%20until%20it%20became%20a%20museum%20under%20Ataturk%20in%201931%2C%20before%20being%20changed%20back%20to%20a%20mosque%20by%20the%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%20government%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20the%202023%20election%2C%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al-monitor.com%2Foriginals%2F2023%2F05%2Ferdogan-leads-prayers-eve-fight-political-life%5C%22%3Eled%20prayers%20at%20the%20Hagia%20Sophia%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20same%20fashion%20that%20Ottoman%20sultans%20had%20done%20centuries%20before%20as%20their%20troops%20headed%20off%20to%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29080610%2FFxQCVVsWYAIDTu2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29080610%2FFxQCVVsWYAIDTu2.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29080610%2FFxQCVVsWYAIDTu2-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29080610%2FFxQCVVsWYAIDTu2-1024x689.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-655372%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22808%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETurkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20after%20the%20election%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20May%2028%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40RTErdogan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20echoes%20of%20the%20Ottoman%20Empire%20continue%20to%20ring.%20Turkey%20has%20always%20been%20striving%20for%20modernity%20and%20its%20record%20can%20be%20read%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20global%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2018th%20century%2C%20there%20were%20plans%20to%20reform%20the%20intersection%20of%20education%2C%20administration%2C%20and%20social%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20significant%20changed%20in%20these%20areas%20until%20the%20establishment%20of%20modern%20Turkey%20under%20Ataturk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Ataturk%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F26301074%5C%22%3Eunique%20state-society-religion%20relations%3C%2Fa%3E%20developed%3A%20a%20Turkish%20type%20of%20secularism%2C%20or%20in%20Turkish%2C%20laiklik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20creating%20the%20Turkish%20Republic%2C%20Ataturk%20abolished%20the%20caliphate%2C%20the%20Islamic%20merger%20of%20the%20political%20and%20religious%20that%20had%20existed%20since%20the%201500s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20many%20in%20the%20West%20believe%20ended%20state%20contact%20with%20religion%20in%20the%20newly%20secular%20republic%20of%20Turkey%20of%20the%201920s%20Ataturk%20found%20an%20organisation%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdiyanet-the-turkish-religious-authority-that-makes-millions%2Fa-50517590%5C%22%3EDiyanet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiyanet%20is%20Turkey%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%20of%20Religious%20Affairs.%20Modern%20in%20its%20title%2C%20it%20is%20still%20a%20body%20that%20closely%20resembles%20the%20semi-bureaucratic%2C%20semi-political%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facuresearchbank.acu.edu.au%2Fdownload%2F18f17d2543736122419b06adf1037557c58d97c079b90e4345f32cd7c3017921%2F267072%2FOA_Yilmaz_2022_Use_of_Religion_in_Blame_Avoidance.pdf%5C%22%3Einstitutions%20that%20controlled%20religion%20in%20Byzantine%20and%20Ottoman%20times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiyanet%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20holding%20incredible%20influence%2C%20funding%20and%20control%20in%20Turkey%2C%20and%20of%20shaping%20international%20views%20of%20Turkey%20through%20its%20overseas%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20fundamentally%20all%20it%20is%20performing%20is%20a%20very%20Turkish%20act%20of%20using%20both%20religion%20and%20politics%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkish%20secularism%20has%20never%20been%20a%20complete%20separation%20of%20religion%20and%20politics%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.academia.edu%2F15166769%2FManagement_of_Religion_in_Turkey%5C%22%3Emore%20a%20political%20practice%20of%20controlling%20religion%20and%20aligning%20its%20sphere%20with%20its%20own%20wishes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intricate%20relationship%20of%20managing%20religion%20among%20politics%20and%20wider%20society%20in%20Turkey%20did%20not%20begin%20with%20the%20Republican%20period%20but%20continued%20a%20longer%20legacy%20aligned%20with%20global%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Justice%20and%20Development%20Party%20era%20and%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%2C%20the%20two-way%20relationship%20has%20re-emerged%20between%20religion%20and%20political%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20has%20become%20much%20more%20repressive%2C%20has%20begun%20to%20monopolise%20religion%20and%20gets%20its%20legitimacy%20from%20the%20religious%20discourse%20within%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Sunni%20Islamic%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20those%2C%20the%20Diyanet%20is%20critical%20as%20one%20of%20the%20visible%20faces%20of%20political%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20and%20Development%20Party%20period%20is%20primarily%20distinguished%20by%20the%20establishment%20of%20hegemony%20over%20religion%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20traumatic%20struggle%20with%20the%20G%C3%BClen%20Movement%20and%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20state%20identity%20after%20the%202016%20coup%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wilsoncenter.org%2Farticle%2Fprofile-fethullah-gulen%5C%22%3EFetullah%20G%C3%BClen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20cleric%20the%20Turkish%20government%20claims%20was%20behind%20the%20failed%20coup%20attempt%2C%20spent%20decades%20as%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%20along%20his%20road%20to%20supremacy.%20When%20their%20objectives%20differed%2C%20G%C3%BClen%E2%80%99s%20organisation%20and%20followers%20were%20imprisoned%20or%20fled%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErdo%C4%9Fan%20is%20now%20set%20to%20continue%20to%20shape%20Turkey%20through%20his%20narrow%20lens%20of%20religion%20being%20leveraged%20for%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20and%20the%20clash%20with%20G%C3%BClen%20are%20just%20another%20reflection%20of%20the%20instrumentalization%20of%20Islam%20as%20a%20tool%20by%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20whose%20leading%20supporters%20are%20largely%20religious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepression%20of%20all%20opposition%20groups%20through%20the%20monopolised%20religion%20is%20easy%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Turkey%20where%20it%20brings%20a%20low%20political%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20might%20argue%20that%20the%20Kemalists%20of%20the%20early%20republican%20years%20controlled%20public%20religious%20manifestation%20through%20restrictive%20measures%20while%20the%20Justice%20Action%20Party%20is%20regulating%20the%20public%20space%20by%20infusing%20religious%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20control%20over%20religion%20remains%20unchanged%2C%20but%20its%20uses%20have%20become%20much%20more%20comprehensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhttps%2F%2Fwww.londonmet.ac.uk%2Fprofiles%2Fstaff%2Fahmet-erdi-ozturk%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAhmet%20Erdi%20%C3%96zt%C3%BCrk%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20in%20politics%20and%20international%20relations%20at%20London%20Metropolitan%20University%2C%20currently%20working%20as%20the%20Marie%20Sklodowska-Curie%20fellow%20at%20Coventry%20University%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20GIGA%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%2F%5C%22%3E360info%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692716395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22154700%2F1280px-Aya_Sophia_7144824757.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-religion-still-means-power-in-secular-turkey%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Turkish%20Republic%20turns%20100%2C%20the%20modern%20nation%20built%20from%20the%20ashes%20of%20the%20Ottoman%20empire%20continues%20to%20wield%20the%20religious%20power%20of%20its%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-religion-still-means-power-in-secular-turkey%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%