Lalu%E2%80%99s%20Bail%20After%20One%20and%20A%20Half%20years%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22160042%2FF1Qj0rPaAAA7yFs.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPatna%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20bail%2C%20almost%20one%20and%20half%20years%20after%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20granted%20him%20relief%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flalu-prasad-gets-bail-in-fifth-fodder-scam-case%5C%22%3Efodder%20scam%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CBI%20petitioned%20the%20apex%20court%20on%20August%2018%20to%20cancel%20bail%20to%20Lalu%20on%20the%20plea%20that%20he%20had%20not%20completed%20half%20of%20his%20sentence%20in%20the%20prison.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20the%20matter%20later%20this%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20granted%20regular%20bail%20to%20Lalu%20in%20April%202022%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20latter%20had%20spent%20half%20of%20his%20sentence%20in%20the%20five%20fodder%20scam%20cases.%20The%20HC%20had%20granted%20him%20bail%20under%20section%20of%20436-A%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20(CrPC)%20supported%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20directive%20to%20grant%20the%20same%20to%20the%20accused%20concerned%20if%20they%20had%20completed%20half%20of%20the%20sentence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lower%20court%20concerned%20had%20convicted%20him%20for%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20in%20five%20cases%20of%20the%20scam%20from%202013%20to%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20the%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20move%20has%20puzzled%20and%20distressed%20his%20supporters%20and%20many%20sections%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20political%20circles%20across%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Jharkhand%20HC%20had%20rejected%20bail%20to%20Lalu%20twice%20after%20the%20CBI%20opposed%20it%20on%20the%20plea%20that%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20completed%20half%20of%20the%20term.%20It%20granted%20him%20bail%20only%20after%20it%20was%20fully%20satisfied%20that%20Lalu%20had%20lived%20in%20the%20jail%20beyond%20half%20of%20his%20sentence%E2%80%9D%2C%20Dev%20Prakash%2C%20senior%20Patna%20high%20court%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCBI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ene%20upar%20waalon%20ke%20nirdesh%20par%20aisa%20kiya%20hoga%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(%E2%80%98the%20CBI%20might%20have%20done%20it%20at%20the%20instruction%20of%20higher%20ups%20%E2%80%93%20read%20political%20masters)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dev%20Prakash%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20lawyers%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20and%20Patna%20high%20courts%20this%20writer%20spoke%20to%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20cancellation%20of%20bail%20would%20be%20a%20rare%20move.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20the%20power%20to%20cancel%20the%20accused%20person%E2%80%99s%20bail%20in%20case%20of%20the%20latter%20violating%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20bail.%20The%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20plea%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20stand%20in%20the%20SC%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Ranchi%20based%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELalu%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20reacting%20to%20the%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20move%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20cowed%20down%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eladengein%20aur%20jitengein%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(%E2%80%98we%20will%20fight%20and%20win%E2%80%99).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20After%20the%20CBI%20moved%20the%20SC%20against%20Lalu%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%20rushed%20to%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20home%20at%20Patna%2C%20to%20express%20his%20solidarity%20with%20the%20RJD%20chief.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flalu-prasad-yadav-birthday-nitish-socialist%5C%22%3EHow%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20Never%20Lost%20His%20Political%20Relevance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdeological%20Narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20gaining%20in%20strength%20and%20consolidating%20its%20position%2C%20it%20would%20appear%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20anxious%20and%20even%20jittery%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20anti-BJP%20forces%20can%20have%20a%20direct%20bearing%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20prospects.%20Political%20observers%20believe%20that%20the%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20action%20against%20Lalu%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20design%E2%80%9D%20to%20destabilise%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%20%E2%80%93%20a%20significant%20leader%20of%20INDIA%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20focusing%20on%20building%20an%20ideological%20narrative%20against%20Narendra%20Modi.%20A%20day%20after%20the%20PM%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20time%20and%20energy%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20against%20the%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20the%20Bihar%20CM%20landed%20in%20Delhi%20to%20pay%20his%20tribute%20to%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20on%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20death%20anniversary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20never%20forget%20Vajpayee%20ji.%20He%20made%20me%20a%20member%20of%20his%20cabinet%20and%20played%20the%20pivotal%20role%20in%20making%20me%20Bihar%20CM%20in%202005.%20He%20loved%20us%20immensely.%20I%20have%20highest%20respect%20for%20him%E2%80%9D%2C%20Nitish%20said%20after%20paying%20his%20homage%20to%20Vajpayee.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20the%20CM%20used%20the%20occasion%20to%20attack%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22160505%2FFzUpwgqXsAENI1n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22160505%2FFzUpwgqXsAENI1n.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22160505%2FFzUpwgqXsAENI1n-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22160505%2FFzUpwgqXsAENI1n-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669181%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENitish%20Kumar%20with%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40laluprasadrjd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NDA%20was%20formed%20under%20Vajpayee%20ji%E2%80%99s%20stewardship%20in%201999.%20We%20were%20all%20part%20of%20it.%20Vajpayee%20ji%20used%20to%20call%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20as%20long%20as%20he%20was%20active.%20What%20he%20(Narendra%20Modi)%20has%20to%20do%20with%20NDA%3F%20He%20(Modi)%20never%20called%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20meet%20after%20he%20became%20PM%20in%202014.%20Now%20he%20is%20calling%20it%20after%20we%20have%20formed%20INDIA%E2%80%9D%2C%20Nitish%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20MP%20(Rajya%20Sabha)%2C%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNitish%20by%20praising%20Atal%20ji%20(A%20B%20Vajpayee)-L%20K%20Advani%2C%20and%20attacking%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20division%20in%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20work%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESushil%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20a%20veteran%20leader%20equipped%20with%20experience%20to%20read%20and%20understand%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20is%20largely%20correct%20in%20his%20observation.%20Nitish%2C%20perhaps%2C%20knows%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20large%20number%20of%20leaders%20grown%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98tutelage%E2%80%99%20of%20Vajpayee%20and%20L%20K%20Advani%2C%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20Modi%20injecting%20excessive%20militancy%20and%20hate%20against%20the%20minorities%20among%20the%20BJP%20cadres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20paying%20tribute%20to%20Vajpayee%20at%20his%20death%20anniversary%20the%20%E2%80%9Castute%E2%80%9D%20Bihar%20CM%20has%20addressed%20to%20%E2%80%98liberal%20sections%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20indicating%20that%20he%20was%20not%20opposed%20to%20the%20BJP%20as%20whole%2C%20but%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctotalitarian%E2%80%9D%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PM%2C%20perhaps%2C%20is%20still%20struggling%20about%20how%20exactly%20to%20counter%20INDIA%20alliance%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20Nitish%2C%20and%20particularly%20Hindi-belt%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20on%20ideological%20issues.%20The%20INDIA%20parties%20have%20repeatedly%20accused%20Modi%20and%20his%20aide%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20of%20misusing%20the%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20against%20their%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-questions-raised-over-selective-pursuit-of-opposition-by-investigative-agencies%5C%22%3EBihar%3A%20Questions%20Raised%20Over%20Selective%20Pursuit%20of%20Opposition%20by%20Investigative%20Agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBI%20and%20ED%20Tango%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20consistently%20maintained%20by%20the%20opposition%20that%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20been%20brazenly%20using%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20against%20its%20political%20opponents.%20Four%20days%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20extended%20the%20service%20of%20its%20director%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%20till%20September%2015%2C%20the%20ED%20attached%20the%20property%20of%20Lalu%20and%20his%20family%20members%20worth%20Rs%20six%20crore%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20current%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CBI%20and%20ED%20are%20relentless%20against%20Lalu%20and%20his%20family%20after%20Nitish%20dumped%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20Left%20parties%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20CBI%20and%20ED%20had%20opened%20two%20railways%20related%20cases%20against%20the%20family%2C%20despite%20the%20cases%20having%20been%20closed%2C%20and%20have%20raided%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20property%2C%20questioned%20Tejashwi%2C%20their%20family%20members%20and%20have%20framed%20them%20in%20multiple%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20had%20so%20far%20been%20pursuing%20the%20cases%20related%20to%20the%20Railways%20against%20Lalu%20and%20family.%20They%20were%20silent%20on%20the%20fodder%20scam%20after%20Lalu%20had%20secured%20regular%20bail%20in%20it%20in%20April%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20CBI%20having%20suddenly%20found%20reasons%20to%20question%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20bail%2C%20just%20months%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20should%20be%20no%20surprise%20to%20INDIA%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20on%20folklore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692703838000%2C%22visual%22%3A