w.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-66582425%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amarnath%20Yatra%20Suspended%20for%20'Urgent%20Repairs'%20After%20Number%20of%20Pilgrims%20Falls%20Dramatically%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F17153230%2FNL1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Amid%20a%20rapid%20decline%20in%20the%20footfall%20of%20pilgrims%20and%20the%20complete%20melting%20of%20the%20ice%20Shiva%20Lingam%20in%20the%20cave%20shrine%2C%20authorities%20in%20Kashmir%20have%20suspended%20the%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20reportedly%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20repairs%E2%80%9D%20that%20have%20been%20taken%20up%20even%20as%20the%20annual%20pilgrimage%20is%20officially%20still%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20considerable%20reduction%20in%20the%20flow%20of%20pilgrims%20and%20the%20urgent%20repairs%20and%20maintenance%20of%20the%20Yatra%20tracks%20at%20vulnerable%20stretches%20being%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%2C%20movement%20of%20pilgrims%20on%20both%20tracks%20leading%20to%20the%20Holy%20Cave%20is%20not%20advisable%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Shri%20Amarnath%20Shrine%20Board%2C%20the%20nodal%20body%20responsible%20for%20organising%20the%20pilgrimage%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sacred%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%2C%20which%20started%20on%20July%201%20this%20year%2C%20was%20planned%20to%20be%20the%20longest%20in%20history%2C%20with%20officials%20expecting%20more%20than%20half%20a%20million%20pilgrims%20to%20pay%20obeisance%20at%20the%20cave%20shrine%20located%20in%20the%20high%20mountains%20of%20south%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purported%20aim%20of%20stretching%20the%20pilgrimage%20in%20the%20environmentally-fragile%20Himalayas%2C%20which%20are%20the%20hotspots%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20was%20to%20showcase%20%E2%80%9Cnormalcy%E2%80%9D%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1930299%5C%22%3Ehas%20termed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20record-duration%20pilgrimage%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Creflection%20of%20government%E2%80%99s%20confidence%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20situation%20following%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20elaborate%20arrangements%20were%20made%20for%20the%20pilgrimage%20this%20year%2C%20with%20dozens%20of%20security%20personnel%20deployed%20for%20the%20security%20of%20each%20pilgrim%20as%20they%20made%20their%20way%20from%20Jammu%20to%20the%20cave%20shrine%20in%20south%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20security%20concerns%2C%20locals%20in%20Kashmir%20were%20subject%20to%20grave%20inconvenience%2C%20with%20no%20civilian%20vehicle%20allowed%20to%20move%20on%20the%20roads%20when%20the%20convoys%20of%20the%20pilgrims%20proceeded%20from%20Jammu%20towards%20the%20cave%20shrine%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20six%20base%20hospitals%20were%20set%20up%20along%20the%20twin%20routes%20to%20the%20cave%20shrine%20with%20thousands%20of%20security%20forces%20monitoring%20the%20movement%20of%20pilgrims%20using%20drones%2C%20choppers%20and%20RFID%20tags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20had%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20pilgrims%20will%20open%20more%20opportunities%20for%20livelihood%20for%20locals%20and%20will%20help%20boost%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20economy%20further%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Hindu%20devotees%20who%20paid%20obeisance%20was%20in%20five%20figures%2C%20with%20even%20the%20official%20spokesperson%20issuing%20daily%20bulletins%20about%20the%20attendance%20recorded%20at%20the%20cave%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20August%2C%20the%20number%20of%20pilgrims%20started%20to%20dwindle%2C%20with%20only%20984%20pilgrims%20leaving%20Jammu%20base%20camp%20to%20perform%20the%20pilgrimage%20on%20August%202%20from%20both%20Chandanwari%20and%20Baltal%20routes%20to%20the%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20August%2021%2C%20the%20number%20came%20down%20further%20to%20just%20362%2C%20with%20no%20pilgrim%20opting%20to%20undertake%20the%20pilgrimage%20from%20the%20Pahalgam%20route%2C%20the%20longest%20among%20the%20twin%20routes%20leading%20to%20the%20cave%20shrine%20which%20is%20located%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%203%2C888%20m%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Lidder%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20dismay%2C%20the%20ice%20Shivalingam%20in%20the%20cave%20shrine%20has%20melted%20completely%20%E2%80%94%20much%20earlier%20(in%20July)%20as%20compared%20to%20previous%20years%20%E2%80%94%20because%20of%20hot%20weather%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Famarnath-yatra-to-remain-temporarily-suspended-from-august-23%2Farticleshow%2F102881035.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20clear%20explanation%20on%20the%20need%20for%20undertaking%20repairs%20of%20the%20tracks%20leading%20to%20the%20shrine%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%2C%20even%20though%20the%20weather%20has%20been%20relatively%20favourable%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20holy%20mace%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20(Chari%20Mubarak)%20shall%20proceed%20towards%20the%20traditional%20Pahalgam%20route%20as%20per%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20prayer%20session%20or%20%E2%80%98Chhari-Pujan%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20holy%20mace%20was%20performed%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Nag%20Panchami%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2021%2C%20at%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Shri%20Amareshwar%20Temple%20in%20Mahadev%20Gir%20Dashnami%20Akhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahant%20Deependra%20Giri%2C%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20mace%2C%20will%20carry%20the%20mace%20to%20the%20Amarnath%20cave%20shrine%20with%20night%20halts%20planned%20in%20Pahalgam%20on%20August%2026-27%2C%20Chandanwari%20on%20August%2028%2C%20Sheshnag%20on%20August%2029%20and%20Panchtarni%20on%20August%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20a%20special%20prayer%20and%20darshan%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20Shravan%20Purnima%20on%20August%2031%20at%20the%20shrine%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20pilgrimage%20has%20seen%20%E2%80%9Coverwhelming%20footfall%E2%80%9D%20this%20year%20with%20more%20than%204.4%20lakh%20pilgrims%20having%20paid%20obeisance%20at%20the%20shrine%20so%20far%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9C43%20pilgrims%20have%20died%20due%20to%20natural%20causes%20or%20accidents%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20cloudburst%20struck%20the%20base%20camp%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%20near%20the%20cave%20shrine%2C%20killing%2016%20pilgrims%20while%2040%20pilgrims%20were%20reported%20missing%2C%20prompting%20officials%20to%20revise%20the%20route%20plan%20for%20the%20pilgrims%20proceeding%20to%20the%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%203.85%20lakh%20pilgrims%20paid%20obeisance%20at%20the%20shrine%20in%202022%20when%20the%20yatra%20resumed%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20three%20years%20due%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20in%202021%20and%202020%20and%20uncertain%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20when%20the%20sacred%20pilgrimage%20was%20cut%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Amarnath%20Yatra%3A%20a%20Militarised%20Pilgrimage%E2%80%99%20prepared%20by%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Coalition%20of%20Civil%20Society%20flagged%20the%20issues%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmilitarization%2C%20communal%20conflicts%2C%20resource%20monopolisation%20and%20ecological%20devastation%E2%80%9D%20caused%20by%20the%20annual%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20at%20least%20250%20pilgrims%20were%20killed%20due%20to%20excessive%20cold%20and%20snow%20blizzards%20that%20struck%20the%20cave%20shrine%2C%20prompting%20the%20then%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20for%20suggesting%20measures%20to%20avoid%20recurrence%20of%20such%20tragedies%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692702014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F17153230%2FNL1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famarnath-yatra-suspended-for-urgent-repairs-after-number-of-pilgrims-falls-dramatic%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20had%20earlier%20termed%20the%20record-duration%20pilgrimage%20this%20year%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Creflection%20of%20government%E2%80%99s%20confidence%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20situation%20following%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famarnath-yatra-suspended-for-urgent-repairs-after-number-of-pilgrims-falls-dramatic%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vodafone%20Idea%20plans%20to%20clear%20about%20Rs%202%2C400%20crore%20dues%20by%20September%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692701818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-07%2F26%2Ffull%2F1627320318-2485.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvodafone-idea-plans-to-clear-about-rs-2-400-crore-dues-by-september-123082200577_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vodafone%20Idea%20had%20to%20pay%20a%20licence%20fee%20of%20around%20Rs%20770%20crore%20by%20July%20and%20Rs%201%2C680%20crore%20as%20the%20first%20instalment%20for%20the%20spectrum%20it%20purchased%20in%20auctions%20that%20were%20held%20last%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompani