t%20officials%20summoned%20to%20court%20in%20various%20cases%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentres-draft-sop-wants-judiciary-to-treat-government-officials-summoned-to-court-more-congenially%2Farticle67202080.ece%5C%22%3Emore%20congenially%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20particularly%20in%20contempt%20of%20court%20cases.%20The%20note%20says%20that%20government%20officials%20are%20being%20summoned%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cslightest%20of%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20while%20suggesting%20a%20set%20of%20sweeping%20proposals%20with%20regard%20to%20judicial%20proceedings%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20government%20is%20a%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20the%20draft%20SOP%20note%2C%20Mehta%2C%20for%20the%20government%2C%20sought%20to%20clarify%20that%20there%20is%20no%20intention%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20government%20to%20change%20the%20courts%E2%80%99%20power%20of%20judicial%20review.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20note%20in%20question%20only%20refers%20to%20how%20senior%20government%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20chief%20secretaries%2C%20are%20being%20summoned%20by%20courts%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cslightest%20reason%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20agreed%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20view%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20frame%20%E2%80%9Cbroad%20yardsticks%E2%80%9D%20on%20how%20government%20officials%20should%20be%20summoned%20by%20courts.%20He%20also%20concurred%20with%20the%20argument%20made%20in%20the%20draft%20SOP%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20bar%20on%20the%20courts%20from%20summoning%20officials%20when%20the%20case%20is%20still%20pending%20an%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20pointed%20to%20the%20way%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPWqgfugVn1w%5C%22%3Ejudges%20pull%20up%20officers%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20not%20following%20a%20dress%20code%20while%20visiting%20courts.%20%E2%80%9CGovernment%20officials%20are%20not%20officers%20of%20the%20court%20and%20there%20should%20be%20no%20objection%20to%20their%20appearing%20in%20a%20decent%20work%20dress%20unless%20such%20appearance%20is%20unprofessional%20or%20unbecoming%20of%20her%2Fhis%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20draft%20SOP%20sought%20to%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20restrict%20its%20order%20only%20to%20the%20aspect%20of%20issue%20of%20summons%20to%20government%20officials%2C%20and%20nothing%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20various%20issues%20referred%20to%20in%20the%20draft%20SOP%2C%20the%20government%20said%20courts%20should%20only%20prescribe%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbroad%20composition%E2%80%9D%20of%20its%20expert%20committees%20and%20leave%20modalities%2C%20including%20finding%20members%20for%20these%20committees%2C%20to%20the%20government.%20It%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20top%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-sc-to-form-probe-committee-rejects-names-proposed-by-centre%5C%22%3Ehad%20insisted%20on%20naming%20each%20member%20of%20the%20expert%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20chaired%20by%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20A.M.%20Sapre%20to%20look%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-has-the-adani-hindenburg-issue-become-a-matter-of-national-concern%5C%22%3EAdani-Hindenburg%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20note%20also%20said%20courts%20should%20give%20some%20leeway%20to%20the%20government%20with%20regard%20to%20guidelines%20in%20cases%20concerning%20public%20policy%20issues.%20The%20government%20said%20compliance%20with%20judicial%20orders%2C%20which%20involve%20%E2%80%9Ccomplex%20policy%20issues%E2%80%9D%2C%20would%20require%20time%20as%20well%20approval%20from%20ministries%20and%20consultation%20on%20a%20larger%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20underline%20that%20judges%20hearing%20contempt%20proceedings%20relating%20to%20their%20own%20orders%20would%20go%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20natural%20justice.%20Instead%2C%20it%20says%20those%20facing%20contempt%20proceedings%20should%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20ask%20for%20trial%20by%20another%20judge%2C%20and%20courts%20should%20not%20insist%20on%20a%20particular%20outcome%2C%20especially%20on%20matters%20concerning%20the%20executive%20domain.%20It%20should%20be%20seen%20if%20a%20judicial%20order%20is%20enforceable%20at%20all%20in%20contempt%20cases%2C%20the%20draft%20note%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20says%20the%20idea%20behind%20such%20a%20draft%20SOP%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20a%20more%20congenial%20and%20conducive%20environment%20between%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%9D.%20It%20hopes%20that%20the%20draft%20SOP%20will%20help%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20compliance%20of%20judicial%20orders%20by%20the%20government%20machinery%20as%20well%20as%20save%20time%20and%20resources%20for%20both%20the%20courts%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692698405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F02154727%2FScreenshot-2022-11-02-at-3.45.44-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-faults-centres-note-on-courts-conduct-in-govt-cases-says-it-wants-to-dictate-judicial-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20had%20come%20up%20with%20a%20five-page%20draft%20note%20on%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20last%20week%2C%20telling%20the%20judiciary%20to%20treat%20government%20officials%20summoned%20to%20court%20in%20various%20cases%20'more%20congenially'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A70%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-faults-centres-note-on-courts-conduct-in-govt-cases-says-it-wants-to-dictate-judicial-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Subhash%20Ghai%20set%20to%20re-release%20'Khalnaya