0society.%20But%20it%20is%20observed%20in%20several%20cases%20that%20by%20misusing%20of%20said%20provision%20new%20legal%20terrorism%20is%20unleashed%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwomen-unleashed-legal-terrorism-misusing-section-498a-ipc-calcutta-high-court%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20the%20judge%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20criminal%20law%20allows%20a%20complainant%20to%20file%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20but%20the%20same%20has%20to%20be%20justified%20by%20adducing%20cogent%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20quashing%20charges%20under%20Section%20489A%20against%20a%20man%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20specific%20case%2C%20the%20judge%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20a%20man%20and%20his%20family%20members%20challenging%20the%20criminal%20cases%20lodged%20against%20them%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%20in%20October%20and%20December%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20direct%20allegation%20against%20the%20husband%20by%20the%20de-facto%20complainant%20is%20merely%20from%20her%20version.%20It%20support%20no%20documentary%20or%20medical%20evidence.%20One%20neighbour%20has%20heard%20about%20the%20quarrel%20of%20the%20wife%20and%20her%20husband%3B%20the%20quarrel%20of%20two%20persons%20does%20not%20mean%20or%20prove%20who%20is%20in%20aggression%20or%20who%20is%20aggrieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20of%20a%20view%20that%20the%20instant%20criminal%20proceedings%20initiated%20by%20the%20de-facto%20complainant%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20in-laws%20does%20not%20disclose%20prima%20facie%20offence%20against%20them%20as%20alleged.%20The%20proceeding%20are%20instituted%20only%20to%20fulfil%20personal%20grudge.%20Considering%20the%20circumstances%20I%20think%20it%20necessary%20to%20invoke%20the%20inherent%20power%20of%20this%20court%20to%20quash%20the%20proceedings%20otherwise%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20would%20be%20tantamount%20to%20the%20abuse%20of%20process%20of%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F13112951%2FCalcutta_High_Court_-_Kolkata_2011-12-18_0328-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwomen-engaging-in-legal-terrorism-by-misusing-section-on-cruelty-by-husbands-calcutta-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Single-judge%20Justice%20Subhendu%20Samanta%20said%20that%20though%20the%20section%20was%20brought%20it%20for%20women's%20welfare%2C%20it%20is%20now%20being%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Breakthrough%20for%20studying%20ancient%20life%20as%20DNA%20extracted%20from%202%2C900-year-old%20palace%20brick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-clay-brick-history_6258855.jpg%3F20230822093412%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancient%20DNA%20has%20been%20extracted%20from%20a%202%2C900-year-old%20clay%20brick%2C%20potentially%20unlocking%20new%20ways%20of%20studying%20life%20from%20generations%20gone%20by.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A393%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2-900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2-900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2-900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Buzz%20of%20Modi-Xi%20Meeting%2C%20India%2C%20China%20Hold%20Three%20Military-Level%20Talks%20on%20LAC%20in%20Four%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMilitary%20officials%20from%20India%20and%20China%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2021%2C%20held%20talks%20to%20resolve%20the%20border%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20sensitive%20Depsang%20plains.%20It%20was%20the%20third%20such%20meeting%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intense%20round%20of%20discussions%20between%20Major%20General-level%20officials%20from%20both%20sides%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20days%20assumes%20significance%20given%20the%20expectation%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20meet%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20three-day%20BRICS%20summit%2C%20which%20began%20in%20Johannesburg%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitary%20officials%20from%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20entrusted%20with%20the%20responsibility%20to%20find%20a%20workable%20solution%20that%20could%20be%20implemented%20along%20the%20undemarcated%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fdepsang-on-table-india-china-hold-third-meet-in-4-days-537029%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20April%202020%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20border%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh.%20There%20are%20particular%20differences%20over%20pulling%20troops%20back%20from%20the%20Depsang%20plains%20and%20Charding%20Nullah%20near%20Demchok.%20The%20dispute%20is%20concerning%20a%20972%20sq%20km%20plateau%20Depsang.%20Both%20have%20issues%20regarding%20troop%20positions%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20eastern%20edge%20of%20Depsang.%20India%20has%20been%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Army%20deliberating%20preventing%20the%20movement%20of%20Indian%20patrols%20on%20the%20patrolling%20route%20that%20goes%20east%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D%20in%20Depsang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20April%202020%2C%20when%20the%20standoff%20began%2C%20Indian%20patrols%20had%20been%20using%20the%20patrolling%20route.%20However%2C%20since%20then%2C%20China%20has%20been%20referring%20to%20a%20controversial%2030-year-old%20border%20agreement%20to%20prevent%20the%20movement%20of%20Indian%20patrols.%20According%20to%20the%20said%20agreement%2C%20patrolling%20parties%20of%20one%20side%20should%20return%20upon%20encountering%20the%20patrol%20party%20of%20the%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20crucial%20things%20that%20came%20up%20during%20the%20discussion%20was%20that%20the%20Indian%20troops%20would%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Chinese%20when%20patrols%20go%20east%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D.%20This%20means%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20buffer%20zone%2C%20and%20patrols%20cannot%20be%20held%20independently%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%20competing%20claims%20in%20the%20region%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20Depsang%20plains.%20Some%20of%20these%20contested%20points%20have%20great%20strategic%20value%2C%20for%20they%20overlook%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20plateau%20which%20is%20under%20the%20illegal%20control%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20sources%2C%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdefence-india-china-eastern-ladakh-disengagement-talks-promoting-confidence-and-cooperation-for-border-stability-3215648%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Major%20General%