ed%20children%20during%20his%20college%20days.%20In%202013%2C%20while%20studying%20engineering%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20he%20started%20devoting%20his%20weekends%20to%20teaching%20children%20in%20government-run%20shelter%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20classmates%20going%20to%20teach%20students%20in%20shelter%20homes.%20I%20went%20along%20with%20her%20and%20saw%20how%20such%20children%20are%20deprived%20of%20education.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20children%20of%20single%20parents%20and%20from%20tribal%20or%20rural%20backgrounds.%20Coming%20from%20a%20rural%20background%2C%20I%20started%20connecting%20with%20them%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20teach%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20years%2C%20they%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20200%20volunteers%20and%20expanded%20their%20reach%20to%20Bhopal%20and%20Indore%20as%20well.%20By%20now%2C%20this%20was%20no%20more%20a%20weekend%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20NGO%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20lakh%20students%20and%20is%20making%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-150