ure%20and%20humidity%20required%20to%20promote%20the%20growth%20of%20green%20fodder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20regulate%20temperature%2C%20he%20replaced%20air%20conditioners%20with%20his%20%E2%80%98fan-and-pad%E2%80%99%20based%20cooling%20system%20that%20uses%20exhaust%20fans%20to%20pull%20air%20through%20cooling%20pads%2C%20which%20then%20evaporate%20water%20to%20cool%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20summer%2C%20the%20temperature%20shoots%20up%20to%2042%20degrees%20Celsius.%20To%20grow%20fodder%20like%20maize%2C%20you%20require%20a%20temperature%20of%2028%E2%80%9330%20degrees%20Celsius%3B%20whereas%20for%20wheat%20or%20barley%2C%20the%20temperature%20should%20be%2020-24%20degrees%20Celsius.%20This%20fan-and-pad%20system%20reduces%20the%20temperature%20to%20up%20to%2020%20degrees%20Celsius.%20It%20is%20designed%20like%20a%20cooler%20but%20works%20like%20an%20AC%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-2-1692278378.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashwin%20worked%20on%20vital%20parameters%20like%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20required%20to%20promote%20the%20growth%20of%20green%20fodder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-2-1692278378.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-2-1692278378-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-2-1692278378-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-2-1692278378-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-2-1692278378-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327488%5